    <p><xref ref="inv-5-2" text="custom">Investigation 5.2: A moral tale</xref> - Randomized experiment</p>
    <p><xref ref="inv-5-3" text="custom">Investigation 5.3: Nightlights and Near sightedness (cont.)</xref> - Chi-squared test for association</p>
